module REQ_SEARCH_01

/*
 * Alloy 6 ? Structural & Behavioral Model for Formal Verification
 * Requirement : REQ-SEARCH-01
 * Title       : User and Post Search Functionality
 * Type        : Functional
 * Priority    : Medium
